title: HOME FOR RENT 4bd, 2ba
neighborhood: 1757 Minnehaha Ave E, Saint Paul, MN
posting_body: ["Everything you've been looking for and so much more!", 'New Construction in the heart of the east side of St. Paul.', 'Every nook and cranny of this house has been updated with a close attention to detail.', 'Brand new roof, siding, windows, floors, appliances and so much more.', 'You will not want to miss out on this one.', 'The design of the home has been updated to give the rambler style a different layout and feel.', 'The fully finished basement gives you extra living space, two additional bedrooms and a second bathroom.', "City living at it's finest, walking distance to restaurants and markets.", 'Sit out on your front porch and relax or step into your own little oasis in the backyard with some beautiful landscaping.', 'Fantastic move in ready new home just waiting for you to call it home.', 'For more info contact: RANDI L CARR']
